Constructors:
  Constructor help us give initial values th the fields of a class.

Why we should use a constructor:
  1)Constructor help us write cleaner code.
  2)Constructor give us more control over the values that an user can
  assign to the field of a class.
Syntax of Constructor:
  Access modifier className (parameters) {
  we can write any logics inside
  }
Class Dog{
String name;
public Dog{String dogName){
name=dogName;
}